g except the cross of our Lord Jesus Christ. The world has been crucified to me through the cross, and I to the world. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:6:15","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Other mss add in Christ Jesus"},{"kind":"text","text":" both circumcision and uncircumcision "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Col 3:11","book":"Col","chapter":3,"verse":11,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" mean nothing; what matters instead is a new creation. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 1:3","book":"Jhn","chapter":1,"verse":3,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 3:14","book":"Rev","chapter":3,"verse":14,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Col 3:11","book":"Col","chapter":3,"verse":11},{"label":"Jn 1:3","book":"Jhn","chapter":1,"verse":3},{"label":"Rv 3:14","book":"Rev","chapter":3,"verse":14}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Other mss add in Christ Jesus"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:6:16","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"May peace come to all those who follow this standard, and mercy even to the Israel "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 3:8","book":"Luk","chapter":3,"verse":8,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" of God! "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Or And for those who follow this standard, may peace and mercy be upon them, even upon the Israel of God, or And as many who will follow this standard, peace be upon them and mercy even upon the Israel of God."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lk 3:8","book":"Luk","chapter":3,"verse":8}],"footnotes":[{"marker":2,"text":"Or And for those who follow this standard, may peace and mercy be upon them, even upon the Israel of God, or And as many who will follow this standard, peace be upon them and mercy even upon the Israel of God."}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:6:17","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"From now on, let no one cause me trouble, because I bear on my body the marks of Jesus. "},{"k